onumber\] Undo the substitution \[2\pi {\kern 1pt} t=\dfrac{\pi }{6}	ext{, so }t=\dfrac{1}{12}
onumber\] \[2\pi {\kern 1pt} t=\dfrac{5\pi }{6}	ext{, so }t=\dfrac{5}{12}
onumber\] \[2\pi {\kern 1pt} t=\dfrac{13\pi }{6}	ext{, so }t=\dfrac{13}{12}
onumber\] \[2\pi {\kern 1pt} t=\dfrac{17\pi }{6}	ext{, so }t=\dfrac{17}{12}
